{"tid":2435762,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM給的壓力太大？Red Velvet成員Wendy曝多次求助心理醫生：不知道為何努力？","createTime":"2021-03-06T13:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T13:33:25.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9bc52be2d51ec08152d9fd63b5e35b9af8641f","tid":2435762,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2021/03/03/550_1562235_1614727116.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2021%2F03%2F03%2F550_1562235_1614727116.webp&h=00f80059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRed Velvet的主唱Wendy近日在綜藝節目中，表達了自己作為愛豆的真實心境。節目中，同樣來自SM娛樂的Super Junior成員圭賢，表示自己也曾向Wendy諮詢過情緒管理方面的問題。<br />\n<br />\n從小在美國長大的Wendy提到：「生活中的自己是一個非常擅長表達自我的人。但韓國的公司文化和娛樂圈環境，卻只能讓練習生們把自己的想法藏在內心。」<br />\n<br />\n「公司做重大決策的時候，很少有哪位高層了解愛豆或練習生的真實想法。久而久之，我發現自己除了工作之外，逐漸迷失了自我。」<br />\n<br />\n「我甚至懷疑現在做的這一切，到底為了是什麼？」對於Wendy自我感受到的心理變化，現場的嘉賓們認為：「這是韓國偶像們在成長過程中必經的一大重要問題。」<br />\n<br />\n隨著團體名氣越來越高，觀眾對他們的期待也越來越高，加上團體的定位，如果表現出與原先設定稍微不同，就會出現不同的聲音，在追求越來越好的同時，也逐漸喪失了自我。<br />\n<br />\n最後Wendy提到自己曾經多次諮詢過心理醫生，也十分感謝粉絲的鼓勵及理解。她才能重新鼓起勇氣站在舞台上。"},{"pid":"dc989bb21fc466f96aeb8b3a4fa03271150eeef6","tid":2435762,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:17:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.wishnote.tw/share/126252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.wishnote.tw%2Fshare%2F126252&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1nxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=282ea41e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.wishnote.tw/share/126252</a>"},{"pid":"473e280a21195767f6eecf1f0acfc6de80ad97a2","tid":2435762,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hfypAAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhfypAAV.jpg&h=28354849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個樣好似唔同咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a07b00d908c5427209402bf44eb4db1b376b1b","tid":2435762,"uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"473e280a21195767f6eecf1f0acfc6de80ad97a2","tid":2435762,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hfypAAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhfypAAV.jpg&h=28354849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個樣好似唔同咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"跌完爆左顴骨就變左咁"}]}